# Phase gates

Before implementing a feature, identify its phase in `docs/PHASES.md`.

## Phase 0 allowed

- Electron + React + shadcn shell, scripts, builder config
- MongoDB connection by URL, setup wizard, health status
- Settings, theme, logging, event bus, IPC skeleton
- Login/dashboard **UI placeholders** only

## Phase 0 forbidden

- Product/customer/order/expense CRUD
- PDF bills, GST, credit ledger, stock
- Baileys / WhatsApp
- Real auth business logic (beyond stub guard)

Do not "helpfully" add Phase 1+ code during Phase 0 work unless user explicitly expands scope.
